{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01A1qqZRAxvFuQGXyqBiZqpK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now. Looking at the permissions on `/app` vhost:\n- `admin` has `configure=.*`, `write=.*`, `read=.*`\n- `app-user` has `configure=` (empty!), `write=.*`, `read=.*`\n\nThe `app-user` is missing the **configure** permission on `/app`. Without configure permissions, the user can't declare queues. The producer is trying to declare `app-queue` (PUT to `/api/queues/%2Fapp/app-queue`) and this requires configure permissions.\n\nThe fix is simple: grant `app-user` full permissions on `/app` vhost using `rabbitmqctl set_permissions`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":634,"cache_read_input_tokens":31456,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":634},"output_tokens":43,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ff7819b6-5ec0-44d4-8acd-533db9ab2c6b","uuid":"80a1cfff-0afb-4e05-9461-755a615014e9","request_id":"req_011CccPV1L2oRGeze6NkeJgN"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01A1qqZRAxvFuQGXyqBiZqpK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found the problem. `app-user` has empty `configure` permissions on `/app` — it can write and read, but can't declare queues (which requires configure). The fix is to grant full permissions."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":634,"cache_read_input_tokens":31456,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":634},"output_tokens":43,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ff7819b6-5ec0-44d4-8acd-533db9ab2c6b","uuid":"64160bf1-533f-4c60-8a1f-5486a71bdde5","request_id":"req_011CccPV1L2oRGeze6NkeJgN"}
